\description{
Tile plot of patients (columns) x genes (rows) coloured by the eleven
canonical alteration classes (\code{Focal_Amp}, \code{Amp},
\code{Homozygous_Del}, \code{LOH}, \code{Missense}, \code{Truncating},
\code{InFrame}, \code{Promoter}, \code{LGR}, \code{Fusion}, \code{Other}).
When ComplexHeatmap is installed, \code{ComplexHeatmap::oncoPrint()}
renders the output with a top per-patient burden bar, a right-margin
